Development semantics
---

 - block > element
 - modifier
 - packaging: BLOCK = (img* + css + js + bemhtml + md)
Blocks are consistent components with internal structure, associated views and corresponding behavior.

CSS optimizer
 - bem.info/tools/csso
Borschik
 - flattens javascript throught a functionality of including
 - image freezing
BEM trees define block interfaces.

BEM BLOCKS
- are not affected by parents
- do not affect children
- developer
    - names blocks with CSS classes
    - keeps off tag selectors
    - avoids cascade

